  <h2  class="page-title hr-bottom">
    About
  </h2>

  <p>Daniel is a <a href="/resume/">software engineer</a> that enjoys architecture and development
of Java distributed applications, adopts <a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/">Arch Linux</a> w/ <a href="https://i3wm.org/">i3wm</a> as
his de facto operational system (no dual boot), knows what Scrum is about
and believes <a href="https://clojure.org/">Clojure</a> is the most elegant functional programming language ever.
Currently, he is focusing on specialization of <a href="http://kafka.apache.org">Kafka</a>
and <a href="http://aws.amazon.com">AWS</a> technologies.</p>


